			 <h2>Board of Directors</h2>
			  <div id=3D"bodWidget" class=3D"clearfix">
			 =20
											<div class=3D"bodfullcontainer " id=3D"week-2">       	=20
							 <div class=3D"imageBg"><img src=3D"https://pateleng.com/images/bodp=
raveenpatel.jpg" height=3D"247" alt=3D"Patel Engineering"></div>
                            <div class=3D"imageBg1 ">

                                  <img src=3D"https://pateleng.com/images/b=
od/bodBg.jpg" alt=3D"" width=3D"518" height=3D"247">
                                  <span class=3D"bodName">Pravin Patel</spa=
n>
                                  <span class=3D"bodPos">Chairman Emeritus<=
/span>
                                  <span class=3D"closeBtn"><a>Close</a></sp=
an>
                            </div>
							<div class=3D"bodredTitle">                           =20
							<!--<p>// echo stripslashes(html_entity_decode($resultBoards['short_=
description'],ENT_QUOTES)); ?>
							</p>-->
                            </div>
                            <div class=3D"clr"></div>
                           <div class=3D"bod-long-desc"><p>He has graduated=
 in Town Planning from USA and also studied Financial Management from the L=
ondon School of Economics. He is the son of Mr. Arjun Patel, one of the ini=
tial promoters and has a wide experience of more than 45 years in financial=
 management, town planning, architecture etc. Under his vision and erudite =
leadership the Company has acquired immense reputation as an engineering co=
mpany. In addition to guiding the Company, Mr. Patel was instrumental in ac=
quiring two companies in the United States as the Subsidiaries to establish=
 a presence at the global level. He has also been instrumental in introduci=
ng and implementing pioneering techniques in India in the field of construc=
tion industry.</p></div>
                           =20
                             <a class=3D"bod-inner-back">Click here to view=
 other profiles</a>
                             <a class=3D"clickdis">Click here to view Direc=
torships held in  Companies/Body Corporates </a>
        	 	</div>
												<div class=3D"bodfullcontainer " id=3D"week-3">       	=20
							 <div class=3D"imageBg"><img src=3D"https://pateleng.com/images/5535=
3641IMG_5195-g.jpg" height=3D"247" alt=3D"Patel Engineering"></div>
                            <div class=3D"imageBg1 ">

                                  <img src=3D"https://pateleng.com/images/b=
od/bodBg.jpg" alt=3D"" width=3D"518" height=3D"247">
                                  <span class=3D"bodName">Janky Patel</span=
>
                                  <span class=3D"bodPos">Chairperson </span=
>
                                  <span class=3D"closeBtn"><a>Close</a></sp=
an>
                            </div>
							<div class=3D"bodredTitle">                           =20
							<!--<p>// echo stripslashes(html_entity_decode($resultBoards['short_=
description'],ENT_QUOTES)); ?>
							</p>-->
                            </div>
                            <div class=3D"clr"></div>
                           <div class=3D"bod-long-desc"><p>Janky Patel, app=
ointed as non-Executive non-Independent Director, designated as Chairperson=
 of the Company is a graduate from University of Mumbai.</p><p>She has take=
n the responsibility by stepping into the shoe of Chairperson to continue t=
he legacy of excellence of late Mr. Rupen Patel.</p><p>She shall closely wo=
rk with the talented Management team to drive the Company forward. She shal=
l provide the Board with effective leadership in relation to Company=E2=80=
=99s strategy, performance and risk management as well as endure high stand=
ard of corporate governance.</p><p>Ms. Patel shall act in the best interest=
 of the Company and its stakeholders by committing to maintain the highest =
standards for the future of the Company and continue to build on late Mr. R=
upen Patel=E2=80=99s legacy of trust, honor and value of Company=E2=80=99s =
esteemed stakeholders.</p><p class=3D"dirname"><br></p><ul><li class=3D"hig=
hlight">Ms. Janky Patel's directorships in companies/body corporates</li><l=
i>Patel Engineering Limited (Non- Executive Chairperson)</li><li>Raahitya C=
onstructions Private Limited</li><li>Landview India Private Limited&nbsp;&n=
bsp;</li></ul></div>
                           =20
                             <a class=3D"bod-inner-back">Click here to view=
 other profiles</a>
                             <a class=3D"clickdis">Click here to view Direc=
torships held in  Companies/Body Corporates </a>
        	 	</div>
												<div class=3D"bodfullcontainer " id=3D"week-18">       	=20
							 <div class=3D"imageBg"><img src=3D"https://pateleng.com/images/5371=
Kavita_Maam_BOD_1d.jpg" height=3D"247" alt=3D"Patel Engineering"></div>
                            <div class=3D"imageBg1 ">

                                  <img src=3D"https://pateleng.com/images/b=
od/bodBg.jpg" alt=3D"" width=3D"518" height=3D"247">
                                  <span class=3D"bodName">Kavita Shirvaikar=
</span>
                                  <span class=3D"bodPos">Managing Director<=
/span>
                                  <span class=3D"closeBtn"><a>Close</a></sp=
an>
                            </div>
							<div class=3D"bodredTitle">                           =20
							<!--<p>// echo stripslashes(html_entity_decode($resultBoards['short_=
description'],ENT_QUOTES)); ?>
							</p>-->
                            </div>
                            <div class=3D"clr"></div>
                           <div class=3D"bod-long-desc"><p>Ms. Kavita Shirv=
aikar is a qualified Chartered Accountant and a Graduate of the Institute o=
f Cost &amp; Works Accountants of India. She has over 26 years of experienc=
e in the infrastructure sector and a strong background in finance and proje=
ct management.</p><p>Ms. Shirvaikar has been a key figure in the Company=E2=
=80=99s strategic and financial management. Her leadership has been instrum=
ental in steering the Company through challenging financial landscapes, par=
ticularly in areas like debt restructuring, fund management and overall rev=
ival of the Company. Over her decade long tenure with the Company, she has =
been instrumental in implementing key systems and leading major projects, e=
stablishing strong client relationships and her experience in finance gives=
 a fine balance of business acumen and cost controls.</p><p>Ms. Shirvaikar =
joined the Company as Vice President (Finance) and quickly rose through the=
 ranks due to her exceptional financial acumen and leadership skills. In a =
span of just three years, she was promoted to the Board of the Company in A=
pril 2017, reflecting her significant contributions to the Company's growth=
 and stability.</p><p>Before being appointed as Managing Director, she serv=
ed as the Chief Financial Officer (CFO) and Whole Time Director, where she =
played a pivotal role in managing the Company=E2=80=99s treasury, arranging=
 debt and raising equity, overlooking execution at key project sites and pr=
esenting financial statements to the board. Her responsibilities extended t=
o risk management, investor relations, and implementing the Patel Group=E2=
=80=99s debt realignment plans. Under her leadership, the Company has succe=
ssfully navigated complex financial challenges, securing its position as a =
leading player in the infrastructure sector.&nbsp;</p><p>Ms. Kavita Shirvai=
kar=E2=80=99s journey from a finance professional to the Managing Director =
of Patel Engineering is a testament to her exceptional skills, dedication, =
and leadership. Her contributions to the Company and the broader finance in=
dustry have been widely recognized, and she continues to play a pivotal rol=
e in shaping the future of the Company. As the Company continues to grow an=
d evolve, Ms. Shirvaikar=E2=80=99s leadership will be instrumental in navig=
ating the challenges and opportunities that lie ahead.</p><ul><li>Ms.&nbsp;=
<span lang=3D"EN-US">Kavita Shirvaikar</span>'s directorships in companies/=
body corporates:</li><li>Patel Engineering Limited (Managing Director)</li>=
<li>Bellona Estate Developers Limited</li><li>Patel KNR Infrastructures Lim=
ited</li><li>Patel KNR Heavy Infrastructures Limited</li><li>Hampus Infrast=
ructure Private Limited</li><li>Saskang Rong Energy Private Limited</li><li=
>Meyong Hydro Power Private Limited</li><li>Digin Hydro Power Private Limit=
ed</li><li>West Kameng Energy Private Limited</li><li>Sanjukavi Properties =
LLP(Designated Patner)</li></ul></div>
                           =20
