description'],ENT_QUOTES)); ?>
							</p>-->
                            </div>
                            <div class=3D"clr"></div>
                           <div class=3D"bod-long-desc"><p class=3D"xmsonor=
mal">Kishan Lal Daga, an accomplished civil engineer, brings with him a wea=
lth of experience spanning five decades, both domestically and internationa=
lly. He has experience in construction industry and among these overseas ex=
perience in Dubai, Tashkent, Muscat, Mauritius and Mozambique. Business dev=
elopment in construction sector as well as other areas for the overall grow=
th of company in technical, commercial as well as human resource areas. He =
was also associated with Indo African chamber of commerce and Industries as=
 President for almost 12 years. Main objective of the chamber is to promote=
 bilateral business development between India and Africa. He had extensive =
travel in various African countries leading the delegates of Indian busines=
s houses on behalf of chamber.</p><p class=3D"xmsonormal">&nbsp;In November=
 2005, Mr. Daga joined the Company as a Special Director-Projects, assuming=
 responsibilities, primarily, focused on spearheading business development =
initiatives in overseas markets.&nbsp; Mr. Daga, who has been a part of the=
 CMD=E2=80=99s Office, currently spearheads the Contracts department, maint=
aining close ties with the Legal function. In this role, Mr. Daga is respon=
sible for managing contractual and arbitration affairs across all projects =
undertaken by the Company, while also providing oversight on legal matters.=
</p><p class=3D"xmsonormal"><br></p><ul><li><span lang=3D"EN-US">Mr. Kishan=
